It wouldn't be a hearse. No, just the coach and I think six people sat in and they had the coffin on their knees. I - I'm almost certain that was how it happened.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7157778 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110 Do you remember when a child was dead they used to have white reins?
