crowds and watched funerals. Yes, oh yes. That's true, yes. Used to be, you know, it used to be an awful thing like little - 'course then you didn't have a realization of the things as you have now and - see, and if used to be an awful thing to say that M
rs So and So's dead you know, you see, you know - awing thing didn't it to think anybody dead - was dead.
