 that you know and you'd have a black tie but it's only like, as I say, after - after the first world war say, but up to the first world war I should say like it - with the chaps that I knocked about with in Wavertree through the boys Brigade and the choi
r
 I was probably the poorest of the issue you know and - had to do with - and perhaps many times you know felt the position that I wasn't - I was a bit of a blot on the scene you know with these chaps you know because a lot of them like were pretty well- s
