 and - she sent me out one morning to collect the eggs and she had some prize bantams and the cock was a - a terror, you know. And he attacked me this morning and I hit him with a - with this perch you see. I grabbed the perch and hit the cock and of cour
se killed the cock and - grandmother told me that I'd never got to to to see her again until I had the money to pay for a code. I don't think - I think I was in the Army when I paid her for the cock.
