rticularly in the - in the summers of course although as I said like in the summertime in them day's it didn't - provide much - work for a bootmaker because you - you know yourself a lot of poor kids run round in their bare feet in them days didn't they. 
In - some were lucky, the - the police would provide these - these clothes and clogs but - for the most part -
