going to be - perhaps I hadn't better say it because it involves the Liverpool police and - it involves - it involves what I think was the greatest mistake in his life - materially, see. We - we could have been a rich family if - if everything that I beli
e
ve had come off, you see, because - as - as a consequence of what this incident - solicitors from all over England wrote to him and asked him - asked him to take the case up and he refused. Yes. And I think it was only because of his previous association 
