shoes parents - perhaps one parent had died you know and I - I remember - I've got one lad in me mind now who only had a mother and - he used to play football in his bare feet and I think that other people who - others of families like who couldn't say sc
rape an old pair of boots and that up or something, used to help - those sort of things - you used - I - I think on the whole people helped one another better them days than -
