Very well. Particularly on - on a Wednesday I used to run down from school and be there about ten past four and I only had one errand to do and that was to the bosses house with his order and I'd get a cup of tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7157778 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110 How much would he give you for that?
