Well I think it - in them days when - when you remember that some of the men worked a full week for about eighteen bob a week. Yes, it was pretty -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7157778 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110 What did you do with the money?
