\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4087616\charrsid3029110 Errand}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110  boy. Yes. And - carry out the - the bread you know from the bakery into the shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7157778 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110 The bakery was there?
