s a bakery there and it was possible for you to, you know, to learn. As I say I - I had this }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4087616\charrsid3029110 diphtheria}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
