\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8401235 TC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110 Oh I - I think ve
ry well. Particularly because the boss - thought I was pretty observant and intelligent because - I read - in them days they were gas mantles you know, there was nothing else but gas mantles and I read in - in the magazine that when a mantle went smoky bl
a
ck if you sprinkled salt on it it came - it came back - new you see. And when I told the manager this, we had a couple of faulty mantles in the shop, he told the boss and the boss congratulated me and told me always to - you know, remember what I read and
 that sort of thing. And of course those are the sort of things about, you know, found very helpful you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7157778 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8401235 TC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110 Very - very well I would say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7157778 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110 Did you like him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8401235 TC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110 Oh yes, he was - yes, he was very nice chap. 
The manager was - a chap named Shortly and - now it was Short or Shortly - I think it was Shortly and he - he had been a former chorister in Chester Cathedral. He had - he had a daughter who was a wonderful concert - singer. I - I just can't remember her 
name but - she was a wonderful singer and - - at concerts. He had three daughters but this one - was very good singer. And then, like as I say, then after the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4087616\charrsid3029110 
diphtheria}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110  well I went to this Miss Smith. Now -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7157778 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110 How did you like the job?
