Well like as I said earlier, I - I was very disappointed you see in - in the fact - something that I couldn't help there was no - no scholarship at the school - I couldn't have advanced you see for - but the - the - the earlier like you asked me about -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7157778 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110 The next job you went to?
