\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110 
 in people and I said I didn't think very much but I forgot that these people were really - humane - very, very nice people. There were three sisters who'd been left by their father this business. And they - Miss Smith ran the business. One sister was }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1444940 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110 
 and the other sister was given to epilepsy and of course couldn't be left but she did the - the household work and - and super - and they - they employed a maid as well but she did the majority of the household work and t
hey - they were a really wonderful family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7157778 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4223140\charrsid3029110 How did you get this job?
