Oh yes. - Because - I think like at that time Mr Owen had begun to be a little more choosy like in the people a
nd - and I do know that - previously when I was fourteen like, me mother took me down there because I had an elder brother there and they - they wouldn't take you 'til you were sixteen. He preferred you to have had some experience and - of the world like.

