et my standard like of life, you know, I mean you - you know yourself I tried to live as - as I can you see and of course I give some due to the like - when I went to school we didn't even have a - a scholarship at our school. Much to my regret you see, a
n
d the only way in which I learned was in this way with the - with the choir and people you met and we had a wonderful choirmaster you know. He was a German and - yes - and you write - you find his hymn tues - Hervert E Kinsey, he was a wonderful - a wonde
rful voice production specialist and I should imagine our choir was one of the finest in Liverpool at that time. I - I still do a bit of singing you see like - when we go out with the pensioners I - I still -
